<item>
            <title>[LU-10745] SLES12 SP3 detection is incorrect</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10745</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The SLE12 SP2 and SP3 kernels use the same underlying base version but have release numbers that are indistinguishable.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The SP3 kernel has clean_bdev_aliases while the SP2 kernel does not, so we can use its presence to detect which kernel is used.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It has thus far just worked because the baseline ext4 implementation is more or less the same between them.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
